Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.44,0:00:04.23,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I spoke with your father.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.05,0:00:06.44,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,A—And?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.08,0:00:08.19,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,"Let him do it."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.19,0:00:10.65,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,"Men have their dreams."
