Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.91,Default,old man,0,0,0,,It's for Nobuhiro's apartment.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.91,0:00:20.62,Default,old man,0,0,0,,I left his studio exactly the way it was when he died.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.79,0:00:23.46,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,C'mon! I'll show you what a name is!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.42,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Huh?
