Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.52,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,This building?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.39,0:02:08.39,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.28,0:02:10.69,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Ninth floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.83,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I feel kind of nervous.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.63,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,S—Sorry for the intru—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.72,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.30,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's all action hero figures!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.24,0:02:46.93,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,My uncle claimed them as "business expenses"\Nsince he wrote a manga about heroes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.85,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It was a gag manga about heroes, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.19,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Are you making fun of him?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.60,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Just trying to be respectful.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.57,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Try looking behind one of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.65,0:03:01.41,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Jack from 1996? These are ancient!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.91,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,We should read these later!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.91,0:03:06.49,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Seems like he's got every Jack\Nsince it was first serialized.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.49,0:03:09.96,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,And the actual studio's in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.05,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,He has a {\i1}ton{\i0} of comics!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.05,0:03:22.18,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I thought I had a lot,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.47,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,but he probably has a hundred times as much!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.85,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.56,0:03:31.64,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I remember how often I used to come\Nhere and hang out with my uncle!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.40,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,There's more in there too?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.65,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,He always said that reading manga\Nhelped the most with creating it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.99,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,That might have just been him\Nthough, since he sucked at drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.20,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,There's some raw manuscripts here too, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.53,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Can we look through them?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.37,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Sure. I think they were in this closet—
