Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.67,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Is it really okay to look through them?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.67,0:03:57.46,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.59,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What should I pick?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.13,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Guess I'll just start with number one.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.06,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I've never seen a raw manuscript before.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.68,0:04:15.27,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Manuscripts are important too, but\Nyou should look at these names first.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.32,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,You divide the page into frames, make\Nrough sketches and add dialogue.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.94,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,So these are names?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.07,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Names are like blueprints for manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.41,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I think I've seen these before\Nin manga recruitment ads.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.95,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,First, you draw up a name which then\Ngoes to the editors for checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:34.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b1\blur0.669\fs40.111\c&H070D0C&\pos(873.333,103.62)}Name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:34.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b1\blur0.669\fs33.426\c&H070D0C&\pos(873.333,320.889)}Editing
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.95,0:04:32.00,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,You keep fixing and redoing\Nyour name until it's approved.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.00,0:04:34.87,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Once it's approved, you can start on a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:34.87,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b1\blur0.669\fs18.719\c&H070D0C&\pos(873.333,532.809)}Manuscript
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.87,0:04:40.21,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Some artists can just submit a name for review,\Nbut only after they've earned recognition.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.21,0:04:45.47,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,We have to submit a completed manuscript\Nbefore we can earn that recognition.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.22,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get tha—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.44,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Wait, Saiko! You're really\Ngonna make me do all that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.10,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,A script's not enough?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.64,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.77,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,And wait, you can't just copy\Nthis kind of name either!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.73,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,The frames are small because it's a gag manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.53,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Plus, it's too simplistic.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.49,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,You should base the layout on\Nwhat kind of story you have.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.49,0:05:05.82,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I told you already.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.32,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm not teaming up with you\Nunless you make a name I like.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.74,0:05:13.45,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Of course I can rearrange panels and make\Nother changes when I do the final sketches.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.45,0:05:17.00,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,That's why you need to think\Nof a story I'd want to illustrate!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.55,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You're really incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.96,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.92,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'll really do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.01,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'm kind of super excited!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.24,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko, what kind of manga do you wanna draw?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.05,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I like manly manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.05,0:05:32.06,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Manly manga, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.81,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Which ones, specifically?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.77,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What's your favorite manga of all time?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.94,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,'Ashita no Joe!'
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.60,0:05:44.19,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,"Throw a drilling punch to his core, keeping your\Nother elbow tight like it's locked to your side."
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.53,0:05:45.95,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,That one's a real masterpiece.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.53,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,What's your favorite manga?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.24,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I think 'Dragon Ball'.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.24,0:05:57.16,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's definitely a genius work like\Nwhat you were describing earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.37,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,'Joe' is too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.23,0:06:04.67,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Whether it's manga or novels,\NI'm gonna do a ton of research,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.08,0:06:08.43,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'll read anything, even if it's\Nin the battle or romance genre.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.43,0:06:12.93,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Our story will be even better, if I can expand my\N knowledge and get rid of any stereotypes I have.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.39,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,You really might be able to pull this off.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.40,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You think so? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.40,0:06:23.23,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,My uncle put an entry in for the Akatsuka Award.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.69,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,One of the two highest awards\Nin manga, mostly for gag manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.69,Award,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H436DB8&\blur23.398\t(0,700,0.6,\blur1.337\1c&H1B232A&)}{\fs75.208\frz353.3\move(233.333,59.498,233.333,264.065)}Akatsuka Award
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.69,Award,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H436DB8&\blur16.713\t(0,700,0.6,\blur1.003\1c&H25313E&)}{\frz353.3\move(90,239.33,90,443.896)}Hideo Furugawa Hideo "Nippon Forever"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.69,Award,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H436DB8&\blur16.713\t(0,700,0.6,\blur1.003\1c&H25313E&)}{\frz353.3\move(85.333,421.835,85.333,626.402)}Winner: Satoshi Minamimura "Morning Rush"
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.96,0:06:33.74,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,760)}My uncle went through all the past winners\Nlooking for anything they had in common.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.51,0:06:39.96,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,He deduced that gag and satirical\Nmanga were popular with the judges.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.28,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,And he won.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.84,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,So that's how he won?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.34,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,It was only honorable mention.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.52,0:06:49.88,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,But it's a good strategy if you're serious about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.88,0:06:53.68,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Aren't you already about to do the same thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.89,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.89,0:06:58.43,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Anyways, we should look over these names\Nsince we came all the way over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.23,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,These will be great references!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.23,0:07:05.40,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,The red ink corrections seem especially helpful.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.40,0:07:09.15,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shuujin will be able to make\Na name with an interesting story.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.65,0:07:15.45,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,But I've never seriously tried to draw a manga before.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.41,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.41,0:07:18.75,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.75,0:07:22.29,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Do you think we can get an anime\N adaptation by the time we turn eighteen?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.75,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.41,0:07:26.09,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Well you didn't have to tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.09,0:07:30.68,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,But voice actors become like\Npop stars once they hit eighteen.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.97,0:07:38.14,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,They might make Azuki into a sellout \Nbecause she's cute, and ignore her true talent.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.43,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.19,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I want us to be mangakas.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.19,0:07:48.65,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,And I want you and Azuki to get married—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.65,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Just as much as you do.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.57,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,An anime by the time we're eighteen?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.99,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Towards that goal—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.99,0:07:56.64,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,No—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.08,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Let's make it a reality!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.41,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Shuujin—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.75,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,We can definitely make it happen!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.00,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Hey, Saiko—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.63,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Do you know where this name's manuscript is?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.92,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'd like to compare them but—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.64,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,It should be in one of the boxes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.64,0:08:16.32,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll look!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.30,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'll look too!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.31,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.56,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,But really, how many names are there?
