Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.32,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,All these boxes are stuffed full!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.99,0:08:33.03,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,But only 10% of these became actual manuscripts.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.78,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,No— It's more like 1%.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.86,0:08:40.66,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,How did he even draw this many—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.46,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go outside to make a call.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.38,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,To Azuki?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.34,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I said I don't know her number.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.76,Default-Alt,News,0,0,0,,We're still waiting to hear the government's response.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.22,Default-Alt,News,0,0,0,,And onto other news.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.22,0:09:01.31,Default-Alt,News,0,0,0,,Female fans are hosting events in anticipation of rock star Koogy's debut concert—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.19,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.19,0:09:08.11,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You never call me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.27,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.40,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.11,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.11,0:09:16.86,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I always thought he'd committed suicide.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.76,0:09:20.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He wasn't such a coward.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He was a guy who'd just grit his teeth and do\Nthe best he could, when faced with adversity.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.71,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You'd never hear him complaining.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.09,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.20,0:09:34.38,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Even when everyone was asleep,\Nhe'd be up drawing something.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.97,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Moritaka, have you read 'Star of the Giants'?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.68,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.89,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Then you know that one line of Ryoma Sakamoto's?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.39,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.77,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You always did love 'Ashita no Joe'.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.61,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.65,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Dad, I think I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.65,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.53,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.88,0:10:01.74,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Ryoma Sakamoto's line in 'Star of the Giants':
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.64,0:10:06.50,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,"A real man faces death\Nhead-on, even if he's in the gutter."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.41,0:10:12.09,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,That's when Joe Yabuki completely \Nburned out and became pure white ash.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.22,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,By mentioning that unforgettable\Nline, Dad made me think—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.05,0:10:20.14,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna do things half-assed anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.14,0:10:25.06,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm gonna put my life on the\Nline for manga and for Azuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.81,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,This one's funny. I wonder why he gave up on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.07,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Don't copy it!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.78,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in writing a gag manga about heroes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.99,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.54,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Letters?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.46,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.46,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs46.128\bord0\frz23\b0\c&H44354B&\fnJanieHmk\pos(953.333,541.5)\1c&H2F2234&\blur1.003}Miyuki Haruno
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.44,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,We went to different high schools,\Nso we never got to see each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.88,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,We just exchanged letters back and forth.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.34,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What is it, Saiko?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.18,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Letters?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.18,0:11:07.43,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,My uncle had a pen pal since middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.85,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,A pen pal? That's so old-school!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.85,0:11:11.73,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Then it was a long-distance relationship?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.61,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,No, they were in the same city.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.40,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.72,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It'd be rude to look inside, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.33,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,O—Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.99,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,That's an infringement of their privacy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.26,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.12,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's focus on names!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.28,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I, Mashiro Moritaka, and—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.46,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I, Takagi Akito—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.46,0:11:36.27,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,do solemnly swear to keep the \Ncontents of these letters to ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.17,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,We swear!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.37,0:11:41.55,Default-Italic,girl-text,0,0,0,,"Mashiro, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.55,0:11:44.09,Default-Italic,girl-text,0,0,0,,I've finally gotten used to this school.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.09,0:11:49.68,Default-Italic,girl-text,0,0,0,,To describe my classes briefly, they're just\Nlike that old drama, 'Youth: Take Wing!'
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.35,Default-Italic,girl-text,0,0,0,,I went to The Alfee concert.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.19,0:11:58.28,Default-Italic,girl-text,0,0,0,,I hate the rainy season, but I bought two\Ngorgeous umbrellas and I love them."
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.82,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's all super trivial stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.91,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Even though they both liked each other, I\N don't think they could ever actually write that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.28,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I don't get that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.83,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,My uncle wasn't a gambler out of self-indulgence.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.83,0:12:13.71,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,He was waiting until he was a \N proper mangaka to finally confess.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.13,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Oh, that's how it was.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.13,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on the honorable\Nmention for the Akatsuka Award.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.80,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Did I mention that I'll be moving?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.51,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the new address once I get there."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.51,0:12:28.10,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's incredible that they could be\Nso understanding with each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.52,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Is that the last letter?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.31,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.69,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,These last two are postmarked a year apart.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.15,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,That means a letter hadn't come for awhile.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.15,0:12:41.44,Default-Italic,girl-text,0,0,0,,"I've kept quiet about it until now, but next spring—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.90,Default-Italic,girl-text,0,0,0,,I'll be getting married."
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.70,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.70,0:12:49.16,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,She has a different boyfriend even though she\Nand your uncle never had a chance to meet once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.37,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs86.907\bord0\frz11\fax0.15\b0\fnBurst my Bubble\move(626.667,227.296,626,227.296)\blur1.003\t(\fscx109\fscy109)\c&H807279&}married
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.52,0:12:57.71,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I wonder how my uncle felt when he read this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.56,0:13:02.17,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,When did 'Super Hero Legends' start again?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.22,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Oh, um—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.93,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I think it's written in the front.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.31,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It was serialized beginning in 1996.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs33.426\bord0\frz-1.4\pos(1066.667,581.611)\fax0\b0\fnArial Rounded MT Bold\blur0.869\c&H26282A&}Compiled from issues \Nran in Shonen Jack 1996
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.97,0:13:12.18,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,So the letter came two years after that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.52,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It became an anime another two years later.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.52,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,He didn't make it in time, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.52,0:13:20.48,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,That said, it's impressive he waited\N faithfully for it to become an anime.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.12,0:13:24.95,Default,Uncle,0,0,0,,But if it wasn't for her, I wouldn't\Nhave given it my best shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.15,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.15,0:13:29.69,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.69,0:13:32.58,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Isn't there still something in the box?
