Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.79,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,A yearbook?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.50,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,My uncle said he couldn't even ask for a photo.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.42,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Just how innocent was he?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.28,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Miyuki Haruno! Let's find her!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.76,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.80,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I—I get it! I'm already look—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.80,Default-Alt2,Takagi,0,0,0,,Her name's Miyuki Haruno!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.14,Default,both,0,0,0,,Azuki?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.07,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's her mom! This has to be Azuki's mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.03,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Man, DNA sure is scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.49,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Being satisfied with just being pen pals!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.20,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You two are exactly the same!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.78,0:14:12.08,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,That doesn't make it a fac—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.41,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.41,0:14:14.66,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go check!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.79,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,How would we do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.79,0:14:18.96,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,We can just go to Azuki's house \Nagain and ask her mother directly!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.96,0:14:19.92,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.92,0:14:24.09,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's Wednesday, so Azuki's \Nin dance class from 5 to 7pm.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.55,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Why do you know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.22,0:14:28.38,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.38,0:14:32.72,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Couldn't we just ask Azuki what\Nher mom's maiden name was?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.68,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna know a lot more?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.23,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Crap, it's my parents.
