Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.35,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.35,0:14:40.94,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Just what time do you think it is?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.73,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.29,Default,girl,0,0,0,,I'm going to Koogy's concert once exams are over.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.92,Default,girl2,0,0,0,,You got a ticket to the dome? No fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.34,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I guess we can go to Azuki's house.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.33,0:15:09.00,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You wanna know more about what\N happened between those two, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.59,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.64,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.40,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Hey, why are we being so sneaky about this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.40,0:15:24.02,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Because it's more fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.44,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I feel like Gevanni from 'Death Note' right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.83,0:15:31.07,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,You didn't hesitate at all today.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.07,0:15:33.37,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,The second time's always easier.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.20,Default,AMom,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.08,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'm Miho's classmate, Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.91,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but Miho actually just left.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.46,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,A—Actually, today we wanted\Nto speak with you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.33,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,With me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.33,0:15:45.92,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's about the mangaka, Kawaguchi Taro—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.93,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Does this reaction mean she's really the—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.93,0:15:56.18,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,And that we, Mashiro and I, want to be mangakas!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.39,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,It's nice to be young.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.39,0:16:02.10,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I'll make some tea for you, so come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.10,Default,both,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.44,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Please, come in.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.49,Default-Italic,MAshiro,0,0,0,,Wow, she really does look like Azuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.61,Default-Italic,MAshiro,0,0,0,,She's so pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.61,0:16:16.20,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Uh, she's the same age my uncle, so around 42?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.12,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,She looks so much younger!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.72,0:16:20.44,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,So Azuki will look this good in 28 years?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.42,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Though at 42, she should \Nprobably get a different hairstyle.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.32,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,What's the matter, you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.17,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.84,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Well, come on in!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.30,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Just sit wherever you'd like while I get the tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.80,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. Thanks for having us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.43,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,This is the living room Azuki's in everyday.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.39,0:16:43.56,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Mashiro, you're Nobuhiro Mashiro's nephew, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.98,0:16:46.06,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Y—Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.48,0:16:50.03,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Your father was two grades\Nabove us back in middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.03,0:16:53.07,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,He stood out quite a bit because he did judo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.07,0:16:53.99,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.86,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Is coffee alright with you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.87,Default,both,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.12,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Mashiro—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.12,0:17:00.33,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean {\i1}Nobuhiro{\i0} Mashiro, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.33,0:17:04.67,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,He drank canned Black coffee\Neveryday to help himself focus.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.21,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,He mentioned that a lot in his letters.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.75,0:17:11.55,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,She really is my uncle's pen pal.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.97,0:17:18.01,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Well boys, go ahead and ask me anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.51,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.89,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Wait, first we—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.97,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.43,Default,both,0,0,0,,We're really sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.43,0:17:28.06,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,We ended up reading all your letters!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.94,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Oh no! That's so embarrassing! All of them?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.94,0:17:31.73,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.73,0:17:33.65,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,She's blushing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.65,0:17:35.49,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,She's cute even at her age.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.49,0:17:39.66,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Then I didn't write too\Nmany embarrassing things, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.96,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Y—Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.96,0:17:44.54,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Your letters were unbelievably refined.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.54,0:17:45.54,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.29,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I didn't really think much about what I was writing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.56,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.56,0:17:53.42,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,He saved all my letters.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.42,0:17:56.88,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,And then you two stumbled upon them?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.89,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Well, what's done is done.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.89,0:17:59.89,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.26,Default,both,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.27,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.27,0:18:08.31,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,While your letters were incredibly refined,\N they were kind of lacking in actual content.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.36,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,You did like him, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.24,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.24,0:18:20.07,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Then, why did you never write that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.04,0:18:24.24,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,It wasn't that I didn't write it, I just couldn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.24,0:18:28.42,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Not only was it embarrassing,\NI also felt it'd be inappropriate.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.42,0:18:31.96,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,We were probably both waiting\Nto tell each other 'I like you'.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.64,0:18:36.72,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,But I couldn't wait any longer. I found a \Nnew love and ended up getting married.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.72,0:18:40.72,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,When Miho was three, we saw on TV—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.72,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heroes are the legends
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.81,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heroes are super cool
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.48,0:18:51.40,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I was surprised to find out Kawaguchi Taro's\Nmanga had finally become an anime!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.02,0:18:54.61,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heroes are the burning energy that resides in you
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.19,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I was so glad, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.82,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,To see the results of your uncle's hard work.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.99,OP-Eng,,0,0,0,,The burning energy
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.82,0:18:59.45,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,From there on, this is kind\Nof embarrassing to admit, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.78,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I used to read 'Super Hero Legends'\Nat the grocery store sometimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.70,0:19:08.46,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,One time there was a short story\Ncalled 'The Romance of a Drifter'.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.12,Default,Amon,0,0,0,,I cried a little when I read that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.72,0:19:15.58,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I was finally able to understand your uncle's feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.38,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,'The Romance of a Drifter.'
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.23,0:19:24.43,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,The protagonist worked hard to become the Defender\Nof the Universe and earn the affection of a princess.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.52,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,He was an incredibly pathetic protagonist.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.24,0:19:32.10,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,But even though he was weak, the \Nprincess confessed her love to him one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.19,Default-Italic,man,0,0,0,,"You're not supposed to tell me that yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.48,Default-Italic,man,0,0,0,,Just wait patiently until I'm the Defender of the Universe!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.11,Default-Italic,man,0,0,0,,And don't just pop out of nowhere!"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.07,0:19:47.08,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,That story was probably a message to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.20,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I thought so too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.04,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Nice one, Kawaguchi Taro.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.54,0:19:55.25,Default-Italic,Mashiro,0,0,0,,My uncle was able to convey his feelings with manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.25,0:19:58.13,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Then can I ask something now?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.13,0:19:58.88,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.64,0:20:03.93,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Which of you is dating Miho?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.39,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Neither of us yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.18,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,In the future though, it'll be this guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.04,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.31,Default,Amon,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.93,0:20:14.90,Default,Amon,0,0,0,,Nerds were never really my type.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.86,0:20:21.40,Default,Amon,0,0,0,,Girls like boys who are kind of bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.99,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,But, ma'am—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.99,0:20:27.95,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,If that's what you like ma'am, I can be that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.95,0:20:29.58,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I'm a downright felon.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.70,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Hey, sit down!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.25,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Oh, that's how it is. Sorry to misjudge.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.21,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It's fine if you understand now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.96,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Nope, I still don't.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.17,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Um, there's something I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.43,0:20:46.68,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Miho still doesn't know that you\Nand my uncle were classmates,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.68,0:20:51.06,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,and that my uncle was a mangaka, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.44,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.17,0:20:59.40,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Then please don't tell her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.16,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I understand. I won't tell her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.40,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,You shouldn't either, Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.40,0:21:08.28,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Y—Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.62,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Takagi Akito.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.62,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.58,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,Mashiro Moritaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.58,0:21:15.50,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.17,0:21:25.80,Default,Amom,0,0,0,,I'll cheer you on from the sidelines while you\Nwork on becoming excellent mangakas.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.84,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.84,0:21:28.80,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.73,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,She was super nice and super pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.48,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,I totally understand why your uncle fell for her.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.11,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Those two were quite the idealists.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.11,0:21:43.78,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,'The Romance of a Drifter', huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.78,0:21:47.82,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't us becoming mangakas\Na lot like 'The Romance of a Drifter'?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.03,0:21:54.62,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Why do you think your grandpa just\Nleft his son's studio the way it was?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.34,0:22:06.59,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,My dad and my grandpa knew\Nthat I admired my uncle's work.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.88,0:22:10.72,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,That's why they weren't against it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.72,0:22:13.60,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Yeah. They thought it'd turn out like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.56,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,No— Maybe they were hoping it would.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.98,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.98,0:22:21.02,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It isn't just you, it's us!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.11,0:22:24.53,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'll definitely make this dream a reality!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.53,0:22:26.61,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,It isn't just you, it's us!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.61,0:22:28.57,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,If I can't do this—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.53,0:22:30.91,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I won't be a real man!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.91,0:22:33.37,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm not a man yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.20,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,Starting tomorrow—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.33,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,No today,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.67,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm gonna work on my own manga drawing style.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.67,0:22:41.04,Default,Takagi,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm gonna work hard on names!
