Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:22.71,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,mirai no rinkakusen egaku massuguna jougi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:28.38,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,is made of all the courage I've mustered up until today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:28.38,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,ikutsumo no kinou no yuuki de dekiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:33.47,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll climb over the tall wall that I never thought I'd face,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:33.47,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,omoiegaita no to chigau takaikabe koe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:39.52,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,and continue my journey, going past the vanishing point
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:39.52,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,shoushitsuten no mukou e susunde
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:45.69,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,This winding road seems to never end,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:45.69,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,harukanaru winding road
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:51.70,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it is the road I personally chose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:51.70,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,hoka no daredemonai watashi ga jibun de eranda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:59.29,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I set my tiny dreams on fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:59.29,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,kasukana yume wo zenbu moyashita
