Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:13.01,Lyrics-Jap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}jibun no sora ga mieru
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.68,Default,Mashiro,0,0,0,,I'm racing towards my goal\Nof becoming a mangaka.
